Class Staff

java.lang.Object
fsmjdoc.Staff
Direct Known Subclasses:
Admin, Manager
public class Staff extends Object
The Staff class represents an employee with specific attributes and methods related to the employee's duties within a branch.

    • Staff

      public Staff(String Name, String userName, char gender, char designation, int age, String branchName, List<Branch> existingBranches)
      Constructs a new Staff instance with the specified attributes.
      Parameters:
      Name - The name of the staff member.
      userName - The username of the staff member.
      gender - The gender of the staff member.
      designation - The designation of the staff member.
      age - The age of the staff member.
      branchName - The name of the branch the staff member is assigned to.
      existingBranches - A list of existing branches.
